THE ROLE
Expand all
•Promote the Test Library to clients and potential clients.
•Manage the Test Library team and any other resources to ensure effective delivery of psychometric assessments and training accreditation programmes.
•Taking meetings to answer queries about testing and to demonstrate tools held in the test library, to both staff and external clients.
•Manage the effective delivery of psychometric tools within assessment and development centres managed by team.
•Manage relationships with all test suppliers and liaise on issues regarding psychometric tools.
•Support the norming of various tools incorporated into the Test Library.
•Ongoing research and development of psychometric tools to ensure leading edge tools and practice are implemented in the Test Library.
•Co-ordinate the Test Library training programme to ensure effective delivery of training courses.
•Contribute at team leadership meetings on a fortnightly basis to ensure the organisation is well managed.
•Contribute to internal development initiatives to ensure best practice within team . Team Day
•Contribute to external development initiatives to promote . Monthly Breakfast Briefings, Conference Presentations, etc.
•Maximize sales performance of Test Library
REQUIREMENTS
Post-Graduate Degree in Organisational Psychology or related
At least 5 years involvement in assessment – design through feedback
Registered Psychologist
Experience using statistical packages and developing norm groups
Qualified on a range of psychometric tools OPQ, WAVE, MBTI etc.
Accredited to run psychometric training programmes desirable
Strong communication skills
Positive, high energy outlook
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
